Step 5	Step 4	pooled background + dehydration-bias + LOO/influence	dehydration_biased_frozen.tsv
Step 6	Step 5 + 外部解释资源	frozen genes + DAP-seq + root atlas	minimal_regulatory_backbone.tsv、priority_validation_targets.tsv
